    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Dust your work surface with a generous sprinkling of <strong>flour</strong></p><p>Unwrap your <strong>puff pastry</strong> and roll it out to 0.5cm thickness with a <strong>rolling pin</strong>,<strong> </strong>then cut into 2<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>strips per person</p><p>Add the <strong>pastry strips </strong>to a<strong> baking paper</strong>-lined baking tray</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1678301575452-x200.jpg",
