            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top each strip with <strong>grated cheese</strong> and sprinkle your <strong>nigella seeds </strong>on top</p><p>Twist each<strong> </strong>pastry strip from the ends in opposite directions until they look like a spiral</p><p>Put the tray in the oven and cook the pastry twists for 10-12 min or until puffed up, golden and cooked through – these are your <strong>cheesey twists</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1678301582965-x200.jpg",
