            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely slice your <strong>brown onion[s]</strong></p><p>Dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong>, <strong>tomato paste</strong> and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span><strong> sugar </strong>in 600ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> <span class=\"text-purple\">[900ml] </span>[1.2L]</span><strong> boiled water </strong>– this is your <strong>tomato stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1678301590878-x200.jpg",
