            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>to a large pot over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped onion</strong> with a very generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>and<strong> </strong>cook for 3-4 min or until beginning to soften</p><p>Once the onion has softened, add your <strong>ginger & garlic paste </strong>and <strong>curry powder </strong>and cook for 30 secs or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
