    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add your <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong> and <strong>tomato stock</strong> to the pot, bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 3-4 min</p><p>Once done, add the <strong>roasted tomato</strong> and <strong>cultured coconut</strong></p><p>Remove the pot from the heat and blitz everything up with a <strong>(stick) blender </strong>until smooth – this is your <strong>spicy curried tomato soup</strong></p>",
